            <br><br>
            <h1 class="text-center">Corporate Matching Gifts</h1>
            <p>Corporate matching gifts are a great way to maximize a personal contribution to increase the impact of your gift. By tapping into an employer’s matching gift benefit, donation amounts may double or even triple!</p>
            <p>How do I get my gift matched?</p>
            <p>First, find out if your company has a matching gift program.(<a href="https://www.dropbox.com/s/44d0amxfi02v98e/Corporate_Matching_List.pdf">Corporate Match List</a>) Each company has its own guidelines for employees, spouses, retirees, and widows/widowers. Most corporate procedures are simple:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Request a Matching Form from Human Resources or your company website.</li>
                <li>Complete and submit the form to your employer or HOW, according to the directions on the form.</li>
                <li>HOW will verify the form with the company.</li>
                <li>Company issues a matching gift contribution to HOW.</li>
            </ul>

            <h1 class="text-center">DONATE BY MAIL</h1>
                <p>If you prefer to make a contribution by check, click and print the Donor Response Form to mail in with your check to: Heroes on the Water, 101-C N. Greenville Ave. #55, Allen, TX 75002.</p>
                <a  class="btn btn-primary btn-lg col-sm-4 col-sm-offset-4" 
                    href = "http://heroesonthewater.org/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/Donation-Response-Form.pdf"
                    target = "_blank">Donor Response Form (pdf)</a>
               
        </div>

    </div>
</body>
</html>